text: Tamara Bojat (; born 11 April 1997) is a Montenegrin footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Montenegro women's national team. ==Career== Bojat has been capped for the Montenegro national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
